contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentLabel: Digital Dexterity: Community, Roadmap, and Delivering Promises
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.linkcon.LinkContentShortDescription: Wes McChristian, Kentico MVP from Kentico Gold partner Americaneagle.com, recently interviewed Kentico's Lead Product Evangelist Sean Wright about Kentico's roadmap for Xperience by Kentico, the growth the Kentico community, and what the latest product features enable for customers and partners.
